  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IOM activities in Afghanistan outlined in the &#x201C;Priority Response and Requirements Afghanistan Crisis&#x201D; appeal. IOM will prioritize this funding for the Displacement Tracking Matrix (DTM) and Protection activities.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Under this grant IOM will provide cash for protection assistance to 700 persons and continue protection monitoring and reporting, screening and case management. The DTM programme will be continuing the roll out of its Emergency Event Tracking (EET) tool nationwide and associated reporting. The project will run for three months.</narrative>
  </description>
